description:

author: CNN
description: Displaced Palestinians in Gaza woke up to inches of water flooding their tents, after heavy rainfall overnight left their shelters and belongings soaked with no way to dry them out. Officials in Gaza have received “hundreds of pleas for help,” with nonexistent resources to meet that need, according to the spokesperson for Gaza Civil Defense. According to the United Nations, more than 1.4 million people in Gaza are in need of emergency shelter items and more than 320,000 housing units have been damaged by Israeli military attacks. #CNN #News #Gaza
title: Heavy rainfall devastates displaced Palestinians in Gaza

title: Elon Musk’s dad: ‘we never saw’ oppression during apartheid

author: CNN
description:
In the 1980s, Leland Vittert’s parents were told that nothing could be done about their son’s autism. But that didn’t stop them from trying. In his new memoir, anchor and reporter Vittert reveals his autism diagnosis for the first time and details how his family, especially his father, helped him achieve personal and professional success.

Listen to the full episode on CNN's Chasing Life podcast: https://swap.fm/l/clsgyt111425

#cnn #news #chasinglife #drsanjaygupta #lelandvittert #bornlucky #autism #health
title: How a father’s devotion helped his son adapt to the world | Chasing Life

author: CNN
description: At least 89 Palestinian patients and their companions from Gaza undergoing treatment in Jerusalem are at risk of deportation by Israeli authorities, according to families and medical teams. Many of the sick patients were evacuated before the war in Gaza began two years ago, and some are now afraid to return to the battered enclave, where 94% of hospitals there have been damaged or destroyed, according to the WHO. While most have agreed to return. The WHO told CNN that the organization had been asked by the Israeli military to facilitate the transfer of patients early next week. CNN Producer Abeer Salman reports on their cases. #CNN #news
title: Israel to deport sick patients back to Gaza

author: CNN
description: Flames consumed most of the facade of the Wenchang Pavilion in east China's Jiangsu province. Local officials said the fire was triggered by a visitor’s improper use of incense and candles. No casualties were reported. #cnn, #news
title: Large fire breaks out at Chinese temple

author: CNN
description: Video from social media shows Cynthia Erivo rushing to protect Ariana Grande from a man who breached security at Wicked: For Good’s Pacific film premiere in Singapore. The man has been charged with committing a public nuisance. CNN has reached out to Grande’s representatives for comment. #CNN #News
title: Cynthia Erivo shields Ariana Grande from barrier-jumping fan

description: Lawyers for former FBI Director James Comey and New York Attorney General Letitia James asked a judge to disqualify Lindsey Halligan, the interim US attorney who brought the criminal cases against them.
